Module org.apache.jena.core
Package org.apache.jena.rdfxml.xmlinput0.impl

Class XMLHandler

java.lang.Object
org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
org.apache.jena.rdfxml.xmlinput0.impl.XMLHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
ARPErrorNumbers, Names, ContentHandler, DTDHandler, EntityResolver, ErrorHandler, LexicalHandler
Direct Known Subclasses:
RDFXMLParser0, SAX2RDFImpl
public class XMLHandler extends DefaultHandler implements ARPErrorNumbers, Names
This class converts SAX events into a stream of encapsulated events suitable for the RDF parser. In effect, this is the RDF lexer. updates by kers to handle exporting namespace prefix maps.
